One Move Captures Black (24)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par This position looks difficult. Black seems to be quite strong.
\par
\par However, black's group has a fatal weak point.
\par A single blow can knock black out.
\par }
