Diagram 1 (Black's Good Response)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If white attacks black from the outside with 1, it is good for black to connect at 2. Up to 4, black lives easily.
\par
\par So, is white 2 the vital point?
\par }
